il.ac.tau.cs.databases.atlas.db.connection

Class FixedConnectionPool

  • java.lang.Object
    • il.ac.tau.cs.databases.atlas.db.connection.FixedConnectionPool
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConnectionPool

    public class FixedConnectionPool
extends java.lang.Object
implements ConnectionPool
    This class is a singleton connection pool (thus the enum) with a fixed number of connections. When all connections are used up, null is returned instead of connection.
